earnings_per_harvest_blueberries = 40

# Total earnings per year
total_earnings_strawberries = harvests_strawberries_per_year * earnings_per_harvest_strawberries
total_earnings_blueberries = harvests_blueberries_per_year * earnings_per_harvest_blueberries

# Sum of total earnings
total_annual_earnings = total_earnings_strawberries + total_earnings_blueberries
print(total_annual_earnings)
```
```output
320.0
```
The total amount of money Samantha can earn every year is \(\boxed{320}\) dollars.
