```
The output confirms that the time spent resting at the 20 km mark is approximately 10 minutes. The slight discrepancy is due to floating-point precision, but it is effectively 10 minutes.

Thus, the time the runner spent resting at the 20 km mark is \(\boxed{10}\) minutes.
