\]
Thus, the solutions are:
\[
a = \frac{-7 + \sqrt{595}}{13} \quad \text{and} \quad a = \frac{-7 - \sqrt{595}}{13}.
\]
So the final answer is:
\[
\boxed{\frac{-7 + \sqrt{595}}{13}, \frac{-7 - \sqrt{595}}{13}}.
