\[
1239 \div 121 = 10 \quad \text{(quotient)} \quad \text{so the coefficient of } 11^2 \text{ is 10.}
\]
We subtract \(121 \cdot 10 = 1210\) from 1239 to get the remainder:
\[
1239 - 1210 = 29.
