\[2(x^2 - 3x + 1) - 5(x^2 + 2x - 3) + x(3x^2 - 2x - 1),\]
we will distribute the constants:
\[2x^2 - 6x + 2 - 5x^2 - 10x + 15 + 3x^3 - 2x^2 - x.\]

