# Calculate the number of rabbits in Maplewood Meadow before migration
R = deer_today * (4 / 9)

# Calculate the number of rabbits that remained in Maplewood Meadow
rabbits_remaining = (3 / 4) * R
print(rabbits_remaining)
```
```output
30.0
```
The number of rabbits that remain in Maplewood Meadow is \(\boxed{30}\).
